---
const pageTitle = "Use Cases | BADINGA Technologies";
const pageDescription =
  "Practical, production-ready examples of how BADINGA Technologies helps organizations deploy secure AI platforms on-prem and in disconnected environments.";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg?v=3" />
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="page">
      <header class="header">
        <a class="brand" href="/">BADINGA Technologies</a>
        <nav class="nav">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/use-cases">Use Cases</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <h1>Real-World Use Cases for Secure AI in Regulated Environments</h1>
        <p class="subhead">
          Practical, production-ready examples of how we help organizations deploy secure AI-ready
          Kubernetes platforms on-prem and in disconnected environments.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="cta-primary" href="/#contact">Request a Platform Assessment</a>
          <a class="cta-secondary" href="/#what-we-do">Back to overview</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Use cases we deliver</h2>

        <div class="grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>1) Secure AI inference on disconnected networks</h3>
            <p class="label">Problem</p>
            <p>
              You have AI models or analytics initiatives, but policy and security constraints
              prevent cloud deployment.
            </p>

            <p class="label">What we deliver</p>
            <ul>
              <li>On-prem Kubernetes foundation aligned to your constraints</li>
              <li>Containerized inference services (CPU-first; GPU optional)</li>
              <li>Access control and audit-friendly deployment patterns</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="label">Outcome</p>
            <p>AI capabilities deployed securely with no internet dependency.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>2) MLOps for regulated, offline environments</h3>
            <p class="label">Problem</p>
            <p>
              Models cannot be promoted safely across environments. Updates are manual, risky, and
              difficult to audit.
            </p>

            <p class="label">What we deliver</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Offline-friendly model promotion (dev → test → prod)</li>
              <li>Versioned artifacts and controlled rollouts</li>
              <li>Rollback-ready releases and traceable change history</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="label">Outcome</p>
            <p>Predictable model updates with governance and operational control.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>3) AI-ready platform modernization</h3>
            <p class="label">Problem</p>
            <p>
              Legacy infrastructure blocks modernization. Platform risk makes leadership hesitant to
              enable AI in production.
            </p>

            <p class="label">What we deliver</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Hardened Kubernetes platform with clear operating model</li>
              <li>Standardized deployment patterns for engineering teams</li>
              <li>Separation of infra, security, and application concerns</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="label">Outcome</p>
            <p>Lower operational risk and faster delivery cycles without cloud dependence.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>4) Audit-ready AI platforms</h3>
            <p class="label">Problem</p>
            <p>
              Leadership and auditors can’t verify how AI systems work, how they change, or who has
              access.
            </p>

            <p class="label">What we deliver</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Architecture and security documentation built for reviewers</li>
              <li>Access and change traceability (who changed what, when)</li>
              <li>Evidence-ready controls aligned to regulated environments</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="label">Outcome</p>
            <p>Systems leadership can defend—and auditors can validate.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section callout">
        <h2>Request a Platform Assessment</h2>
        <p class="muted">
          A focused engagement to evaluate your infrastructure, security constraints, and AI
          readiness—then propose a safe, executable roadmap.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-box">
          <p class="contact-line">
            Email:
            <a href="mailto:contact@badinga.tech">contact@badinga.tech</a>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-line">Primary delivery: Remote (on-site available by arrangement)</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="footer">
        <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} BADINGA Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </main>

    <style>
      :global(body) {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #0b1220;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .page {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 28px 20px 72px;
      }

      .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 14px 0 18px;
      }

      .brand {
        font-weight: 800;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.95);
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }

      .nav {
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .nav-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.8);
        border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
        padding-bottom: 2px;
      }

      .nav-link:hover {
        border-bottom-color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.28);
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 34px 28px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.03);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 2.8vw, 2.6rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
      }

      .subhead {
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
        max-width: 78ch;
      }

      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .cta-primary,
      .cta-secondary {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.14);
      }

      .cta-primary {
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.92);
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .cta-secondary {
        background: #ffffff;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.92);
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 40px;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      .label {
        margin: 14px 0 6px;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.72);
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
      }

      .card ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
      }

      .card li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      .callout {
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 22px;
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.03);
      }

      .muted {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.78);
      }

      .contact-box {
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        background: #ffffff;
        max-width: 720px;
      }

      .contact-line {
        margin: 6px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 54px;
        padding-top: 18px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.65);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
